data.description: Immaculate home in sought after Shady Banks. Why Pay over $3,000/month to rent a 1 Bedroom Apt when you can put your money toward OWNING A HOME! Large corner lot, all new tile flooring, new kitchen cabinets/counters, beautiful new bathroom. Separate Den, Guest Room or Home Office off the Living Room. Impact windows/doors. Freshly painted. Room to expand. Screened porch, Carport. Mini split AC systems keeps electric bills low. French doors in the kitchen & bedroom open to back yard. Located minutes to downtown, Las Olas & the Beach. Hidden gem with one way in/out, surrounded by the New River, no through traffic. 2 parks: Hortt park, 5 acres with tennis, volleyball walking paths, playground, exercise equipment. Bill Kieth Preserve on the River with shoreline, walking trails, picnic area.
